collectionMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Digitised Music Albums, Lyrics and Music Scores
collectionMetadata.description:
This dataset is a list of music albums, lyrics and music scores digitised from the collections of the National Library, Singapore. 

These materials cover a collection of music composed or published by Singaporeans, music produced or published in Singapore, and music related to Singapore.

For enquiries, please email ref@nlb.gov.sg

datasetMetadata.name: National Library Singapore Digitised Music Albums, Lyrics and Music Scores 2024
datasetMetadata.description:
